OL,3,CParents struggling with school uniform
OL,4,Ccosts according to charity
OL,6,FFor millions of children, the new
OL,7,Fschool year seems a grim prospect.
OL,9,FAnd for parents, it's the financial
OL,10,Fimpacts that are dreaded.
OL,12,FNow, campaigners have new research
OL,13,Fhighlighting the struggle many
OL,14,Fhouseholds are facing as the back-to-
OL,15,Fschool bills roll in.
OL,17,FGovernment figures show the cost of
OL,18,Fschool uniforms has pushed 12% of
OL,19,Ffamilies into financial hardship.
