OL,6,FNewly released figures from the
OL,7,FChildren's Society show 60% of parents
OL,8,Fwith children receiving free school
OL,9,Fmeals are struggling.
OL,11,FYet only 22 out of 153 local councils
OL,12,Fin England offer uniform grants for
OL,13,Fthose in need, according to data from
OL,14,FMoney Wellness.
OL,16,FSupermarkets have been in a price war,
OL,17,Fleading to special offers on uniforms
OL,18,F- but many schools still insist on
OL,19,Fmuch more costly branded items from
OL,20,Fspecialist shops.
